data.comment: The match has started.
Falkenbergs awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 1, Free kick for Falkenbergs in the half of Norrkoping.
Throw-in for Falkenbergs close to the penalty box.
John Chibuike puts the ball in the net and the away team now lead 0-1.
In the minute 4, Goal kick for Falkenbergs at Östgötaporten.
Adam Ladeback signals a Norrkoping throw-in in Falkenbergs's half.
Free kick Norrkoping.
In the minute 7, Falkenbergs needs to be cautious. Norrkoping have an attacking throw-in.
Throw-in for Falkenbergs at Östgötaporten.
In Norrkoping, Christoffer Nyman of Norrkoping is presented with a shooting opportunity. But the strike is blocked by the covering defence.
In the minute 9, Falkenbergs push forward at Östgötaporten and Anton Wede gets in a strike. This is blocked, however, by a determined Norrkoping defence.
Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Adam Ladeback.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Norrkoping in their own half.
In the minute 15, Falkenbergs have a goal kick.
Karl Soderstrom hits the post! Very nearly a goal there for Falkenbergs!
Ball safe as Falkenbergs is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 19, Throw-in for Norrkoping in the half of Falkenbergs.
Norrkoping pushes forward through Simon Thern, whose finish on goal is saved.
Corner awarded to Norrkoping.
In the minute 21, An attacking Norrkoping player has been brought down in the area - penalty!
Tobias Englund (Falkenbergs) has received a yellow card from Adam Ladeback.
The match is now all square at 1-1 thanks to a penalty from Christoffer Nyman.
In the minute 23, Norrkoping have been awarded a corner by Adam Ladeback.
Free kick for Falkenbergs in their own half.
In Norrkoping a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 26, Adam Ladeback signals a throw-in for Falkenbergs, close to Norrkoping's area.
Norrkoping awarded a free kick in their own half.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
In the minute 28, Sead Haksabanovic for Norrkoping drives towards goal at Östgötaporten. But the finish is unsuccessful.
Corner awarded to Norrkoping.
Falkenbergs's Karl Soderstrom gets his shot away but it misses the target.
In the minute 29, It's a goal kick for the home team in Norrkoping.
The ref points to the spot, it's a penalty for Norrkoping.
Gregoire Amiot (Falkenbergs) gets a yellow card. He will be suspended from the next match!
In the minute 32, It's advantage Norrkoping in Norrkoping as Christoffer Nyman scores from the spot to make it 2-1.
Marcus Mathisen for the away team is judged to be offside.
Norrkoping have been given a penalty...
In the minute 34, Axel Noren for Falkenbergs has been booked by Adam Ladeback and receives a first yellow card.
Christoffer Nyman gives Norrkoping a 3-1 lead from the penalty spot.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Falkenbergs in their own half.
In the minute 36, Adam Ladeback awards Norrkoping a goal kick.
Ball goes out of play for a Norrkoping goal kick.
Free kick for Norrkoping in their own half.
In the minute 42, Adam Ladeback awards Norrkoping a goal kick.
Throw-in for Norrkoping in their own half.
Jens Gustafsson is making the team's first substitution at Östgötaporten with Alexander Fransson replacing Henrik Castegren.
In the minute 44, In Norrkoping Norrkoping attack through Sead Haksabanovic. The finish is off target, however.
Goal kick for Falkenbergs at Östgötaporten.
Can Norrkoping get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Falkenbergs's half?
In the minute 45, At Östgötaporten the fourth official shows that 3 minutes will be added to the 1st half.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Norrkoping.
Jonathan Levi for Norrkoping gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
In the minute 45, Falkenbergs have a goal kick.
Christoffer Nyman (Norrkoping) is first to the ball but his header is off-target.
Ball goes out of play for a Falkenbergs goal kick.
In the minute 45, The first-half is over at Östgötaporten.
The second-half has started.
Falkenbergs's Anton Wede is on target but unsuccessful.
In the minute 46, Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Adam Ladeback.
Falkenbergs's Gustaf Nilsson attacks the ball with his head but his effort fails to hit the target.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Norrkoping.
In the minute 47, In Norrkoping Norrkoping drive forward through Christoffer Nyman. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Throw-in Norrkoping.
Adam Ladeback awards the away team a throw-in.
In the minute 48, Falkenbergs awarded a free kick in their own half.
Falkenbergs to take a throw-in in Norrkoping territory.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Falkenbergs in their own half.
In Norrkoping a free kick has been awarded the home team.
In the minute 50, Norrkoping's Jonathan Levi has been booked in Norrkoping.
At Östgötaporten, Carl Johansson has been yellow-carded for the away team.
In the minute 52, Corner awarded to Falkenbergs.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Falkenbergs.
Free kick for Norrkoping in their own half.
In the minute 54, Free kick for Norrkoping in the half of Falkenbergs.
Adam Ladeback awards Falkenbergs a goal kick.
Norrkoping have a dangerous throw-in.
In the minute 55, Goal kick for Falkenbergs at Östgötaporten.
Free kick for Norrkoping in their own half.
Falkenbergs awarded a free kick in their own half.
The away team replace Axel Noren with Mahmut Ozen.
In the minute 57, Falkenbergs make their second substitution with Edi Sylisufaj replacing John Chibuike.
Falkenbergs awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 60, Jens Gustafsson (Norrkoping) is making a second substitution, with Ishaq Abdulrazak replacing Christoffer Nyman.
Falkenbergs's Marcus Mathisen gets in a shot on goal at Östgötaporten. But the effort is unsuccessful.
Norrkoping have been awarded a corner by Adam Ladeback.
In the minute 67, Corner awarded to Norrkoping.
Corner awarded to Norrkoping.
Norrkoping move into a 4-1 lead through a Ishaq Abdulrazak header.
In the minute 69, The away team have replaced Anton Wede with Matthew Garbett. This is the third substitution made today by Hans Eklund.
Throw-in Norrkoping.
Melker Nilsson is replacing Gregoire Amiot for Falkenbergs at Östgötaporten.
In the minute 71, Can Falkenbergs capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Norrkoping's half?
Can Falkenbergs get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Norrkoping's half?
Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Adam Ladeback.
In the minute 73, Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Falkenbergs in their own half.
Tobias Karlsson is replacing Carl Johansson for Falkenbergs at Östgötaporten.
Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Norrkoping in their own half.
In the minute 75, Norrkoping awarded a free kick in their own half.
Throw-in high up the field for Norrkoping in Norrkoping.
Free kick for Norrkoping in their own half.
In the minute 79, Throw-in for Falkenbergs at Östgötaporten.
Ball goes out of play for a Norrkoping goal kick.
Corner awarded to Falkenbergs.
In the minute 81, Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Adam Ladeback.
Norrkoping's Isak Bergmann Johanneson breaks free at Östgötaporten. But the strike goes wide of the post.
Falkenbergs have a goal kick.
In the minute 86, Adam Ladeback awards the away team a throw-in.
Maic Sema is on a sub for Jonathan Levi for Norrkoping.
Manasse Kusu is replacing Simon Thern for the home team.
In the minute 88, Adam Ladeback signals a free kick to Norrkoping in their own half.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Norrkoping.
3 minutes of injury time will be added to the 2nd half.
Corner awarded to Norrkoping.
Free kick for Falkenbergs in their own half.
Free kick in a good position for Falkenbergs!
Edi Sylisufaj for Falkenbergs gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
Goal kick for Norrkoping at Östgötaporten.
It's 4-1 as the referee blows for full-time.
Ishaq Abdulrazak (Norrkoping) has received a yellow card from Adam Ladeback.
